relation: Darrow4 - #14 Poo begins his training, which requires deep concentration and meditation. While there is a minor distraction, he has yet to encounter the greatest distraction of all.
Darrow4 - #13 The old sage appears and disappears just as quickly as the wind. What sort of powers will he awaken in Poo? He can start with "turn into a tornado and fly away", for one.
Darrow4 - #12 After some reflecting and interaction with the villagers, Poo reaches his destination. Will the powerful "Moo" training bring him success...?
Darrow4 - #11 Prince Poo, after a few words from his Master, sets out for his final training.

Darrow4 - #10 A plane of existence where all minds and souls can connect... Only those with psychic abilities which have been trained for many years can meet here. Apparently magic cake can enable those who haven't trained to "ascend" momentarily, though. What is in that cake...???
